com.acs.audiojack

Class Track2Data

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.acs.audiojack.Track2Data

  • public class Track2Data
extends java.lang.Object
    The Track2Data class is used to decode the track 2 data into fields specified by ISO/IEC 7813.
